Package game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Key handler to control a Walker.
    DropBullet
    Mouse handler to shoot bullets from a body.
    Game
    The computer game.
    GameLevel
    A basic structure of every level created
    GameLoader
    Loads previously saved state of a game.
    GameSaver
    Saves the current state of the game to a text file.
    GiveFocus
    A mouse listener that gives the keyboard focus to a specified component.
    MyView
    Main view of the game, displaying health bar, bullet count and responsive alerts on the screen.
    PickupBullet
    Collision listener that allows the solider to collect the bullets.
    StopWatch
    Stopwatch that uses the nano time of the system.
    TimeWriterAndReader
    Writes and reads the nano seconds from the text file.
